Windows is a graphical operating system development by Microsoft. This permits users to view and stores files, run software, play games, watch videos, and provide a way to connect to the Internet. 
This OS is design either home computing or professional works. 
The desktop operating system allows user to open multiple windows, browse folders, and open files and applications with the window File Explorer.

MacOS, is other operating system development by the American computer company Apple Inc. Mac was the first personal computer in to use a graphical user interface (GUI), which allowed the user to interact with the operating system by using a mouse to click and drag objects.
